# Every plot and intermediate data file in this directory is generated by
# the Python tooling here (see README.md's "Regenerating plots" section and
# ./regenerate_plots.sh) -- none of it belongs in version control. Binary
# blobs (plots, npz arrays) bit-rot in git history and can't be usefully
# diffed/reviewed; the source (scripts + parameters) is what's checked in.
*.png
*.npz
*.provenance.txt
__pycache__/
.DS_Store
